Package: dscc.mcpserver
Type: Package
Title: MCP Server Exposing the DSCC Cancer Subtyping Method
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Khoi", "Nguyen", email = "khoindd2000@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Exposes the DSCC multi-omics cancer subtyping method (disease
    subtyping via spectral clustering and community detection on consensus
    networks) as Model Context Protocol tools over Streamable HTTP. Provides
    tools to validate omics and survival inputs, run subtyping, evaluate the
    prognostic value of the resulting subtypes (Cox and permutation log-rank
    tests), and plot Kaplan-Meier and silhouette diagnostics. Built on the
    mcpserver R framework. Each analysis runs in a fresh Rscript subprocess
    for isolation; results are persisted to disk and served back as
    resource_link URLs.
